author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
The Death Guard are back with a great new Battle Force and wonderful, very straight forward army rules that push their reputation as durable fighters and powerful de-buff faction that work universally against all opponents. Let's check them out!

Thanks to Games Workshop for the complimentary advance copy of the box, book and cards to review.

author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
KILL MAIM BURN... it's everyone's favourite Bolt Thrower song... WORLD EATER. The Berserkers of Angron's legion take to the field in a bit of a misfire of Codex Design alongside their plague brethren who also have their Codex go up for pre order this week.

Thanks to Games Workshop for the complimentary advance copy of the box, book and cards to review.
